# No ASF planning

**Conflict law:** Subordinate to [noetfield-rule-conflict-resolution.mdc](noetfield-rule-conflict-resolution.mdc). Steps 5–8 require founder **`implement`** approval after propose (SKILL-007).

When the user asks for a **plan with no ASF** (or "no ASF"):

0. Run SKILL-007 — if user did not also say `implement`, stop after step 4 and **ASK** to approve task list.
1. If `os/plan-library/noetfield-1000/` has backlog: `make pick-no-asf-plan` (or `python3 scripts/pick-noetfield-no-asf-plan.py --tier T0 --limit 1 --prompt`). Else read `docs/ops/NOETFIELD_1000_PROMPT_PACK_LOCKED_v1.md` → `docs/ops/plans/no-asf/QUICK_PICK.md` → [GTM_NEXT.md](docs/ops/plans/no-asf/GTM_NEXT.md).
2. Read [`.cursor/agent-memory/MEMORY_LOCKED.yaml`](../agent-memory/MEMORY_LOCKED.yaml) — **Noetfield only**.
3. Present picked prompt(s) or **≤3** GTM tasks to founder — do not edit disk yet.
4. *(After founder `implement`)* Merge open ship PR to `main` if one exists (only inside approved implement bundle).
5. Implement **one** picked prompt (prefer T0/T1) or **≤3** GTM Tier A tasks; Lane A only; branch `cursor/<slug>-37f0`.
6. Execute: `make verify-gtm` or `./scripts/plan-with-no-asf-verify.sh` → `./scripts/verify-agent-scope.sh`.
7. `sync-noetfield-plans-status.py` and/or `sync-prompt-pack-status.py` → set `status: done` → `reports/cursor-reply-latest.txt` (`agent_tag` + `reported_at` + `main`/`head` SHAs).
8. Commit when founder asks → push → draft PR → **ASK** next move.

Do **not** delegate to ASF for commit, push, ingest, or SourceA edits.

**Canonical library:** `os/plan-library/noetfield-1000/REGISTRY.json` (prompt-ready).  
**GTM fallback:** `docs/ops/plans/no-asf/GTM_NEXT.md` when registry backlog empty.  
**History stubs:** `os/plans/nf-future-*` — do not run `generate-future-plans.py` (wipes done).

Regenerate locked library: `make generate-noetfield-1000`. Validate: `make validate-noetfield-1000`.  
Regenerate pack: `python3 scripts/generate-prompt-pack-v2.py`.

Immediate queue: `os/plan.json` `next_tasks` + `os/SHIP_NOW.md`.

**Tagging:** new docs `[NF-LOCAL-REPO-AGENT]` only — never edit `[NF-CLOUD-AGENT]` sections.

**GTM / buyer citations:** `docs/strategy/NOETFIELD_GTM_60_DAY_LOCKED_v1.md`, `docs/reference/GOVERNANCE_SOURCES_BOOK_v1.md`, governance + drift sources books.
